      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-dat-reg-000      thru vis-dat-reg-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ad accettazione data registrazione              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-key-reg-200.
       acc-key-reg-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazioni                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
