                                              (w-wrt-mov-cge-ctr)     .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Riciclo                             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     wrt-mov-cge-100.
       wrt-mov-cge-120.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Flag di regime fiscale particolare      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-te2-flg-rfp (1)    to   l-cge-300-flg-rfp      .
