           move      59                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      17                   to   v-lto                  .
           move      80                   to   v-pto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Video in On                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "ON"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       fnd-tlm-vpl-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
