                                              (1, w-car-cst-iva-ctr)  .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Oltre                               *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     car-cst-iva-170.
       car-cst-iva-165.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se documento in valuta base             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Bufferizzazione                     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-trd-iva-ibl
                    (w-car-cst-iva-ctr)   to   w-te2-iva-ibl
                                              (1, w-car-cst-iva-ctr)  .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Oltre                               *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     car-cst-iva-170.
       car-cst-iva-170.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Imposta                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Calcolo imposta                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DI"                 to   d-imp-iva-tip-ope      .
           move      w-te2-iva-ibl
                    (1, w-car-cst-iva-ctr)
                                          to   d-imp-iva-ibl-iva      .
           move      w-te2-iva-cod
                    (1, w-car-cst-iva-ctr)
                                          to   d-imp-iva-cod-iva      .
           perform   det-imp-iva-cll-000  thru det-imp-iva-cll-999    .
